        "description": "The Dataset of apple stocks has four features:\n- Data\n- Close Price\n-  High Price\n- Low Price\n- Open Price\n- Volume\n\nThe data is ideal for financial analysis, trend forecasting, and correlation studies between Apple and its key partners in the tech industry.\n\n=== About this file ===\n\nAbout this file\nThis .csv file contains apple stock data from 2010 to 2024 and have 6 columns\n\n\n=== Columns & descriptions ===\n\nDate: The timestamp of the stock records in DD-MM-YYYY. Captures day-level trading data.\nClose Price: Close price of the stock on each day\nHigh Price: Highest price of the stock reached during the day\nLow Price: Lowest price of the stock reached during the day\nOpen Price: Open Price of the stock on that day\nVolume: Total volume of the stock on that day\n",
